<h2 class="xl-gap">6. How can I return an order?</h2>
<p>The item(s) must be returned within 7 days of its arrival.</p>
<p>If the product is received back in an altered condition (e.g. a booster box or pack opened, a crease on a near-mint role-playing book etc.), then it will be treated as a used item sold to us, not as a return and we will credit you back to your PayPal account.</p>
<p>You may still be able to sell your item If you are requesting your return beyond 7 days of its arrival, or for an item in an altered condition.</p>
