<h2 class="xl-gap">7. Can I cancel my order?</h2>
<p>Yes, we will be able to cancel it for you provided the order has not yet shipped. Please contact us if you need to cancel your order.</p>
<h2>8.&nbsp;Can I pick up my order myself?&nbsp;</h2>
<p>Yes, you can. However, all pickups need to be arranged prior to make an order to ensure that we can meet your requirements as we are an online store.&nbsp;</p>
