<p><span>We strive to resolve all issues as soon as possible but&nbsp;each case could take 3-10 business days to investigate and resolve. Also, we need to engage with our courier to confirm if the item has been delivered or delivered incorrectly before we could provide an update.&nbsp;</span></p>
